OL,3,CUnpaid carers told to pay back #250
OL,4,Cmillion in overpayments
OL,6,FAn unpaid carer from Kent owed #18,066
OL,7,Fto the Department for Work & Pensions
OL,8,F(DWP) after she said she unwittingly
OL,9,Fbreached Carer's Allowance rules.
OL,11,FElizabeth Moss from Snodland, is one
OL,12,Fof an estimated 134,500 people who
OL,13,Fhave been told to pay back vast
OL,14,Famounts of money because they have
OL,15,Fgone over their entitled hours.
OL,17,FHer son has complex mental health
OL,18,Fissues and she claimed Carer's
OL,19,Fallowance from 2013 to 2020 while
OL,20,Fworking part time in a post office.
