OL,6,FShe admits she wasn't aware of the
OL,7,Fthreshold of a maximum of earning #151
OL,8,Fa week. But she claims the DWP took 8
OL,9,Fyears to get through to her.
OL,11,FMoss said, "they sent me another
OL,12,Fletter saying that if I didn't get in
OL,13,Ftouch with them, they would send the
OL,14,Fbailiffs round." She said she was
OL,15,Fterrified, "I had never had something
OL,16,Flike that before. I've always paid my
OL,17,Fdebts, I have always paid everything.
