OL,6,F"For them to threaten me straight away
OL,7,Fwhen it took them eight years to tell
OL,8,Fme that I owed the money, I was just
OL,9,Fsick to my stomach."
OL,11,FElizabeth volunteered to pay back #50
OL,12,Fa month, as that's all she could
OL,13,Fafford. This has now gone up to #200
OL,14,Fsince claiming PIP because of her own
OL,15,Fdisability. Having made several
OL,16,Fappearances with politicians to raise
OL,17,Fthe issues of Carer's Allowance, she
OL,18,Fsaid it needs reform.
