OL,6,FIf you care for someone for more than
OL,7,F35 hours a week you are entitled to
OL,8,F#81.90 in Carer's Allowance.
OL,10,FBut this only happens if you earn less
OL,11,Fthan #151 per week elsewhere. Around
OL,12,F13 hours based on minimum wage.
OL,14,FIf this goes over, even by just a few
OL,15,Fpennies, you must pay repay any
OL,16,Fallowance in full.
OL,18,FIt's thought 134,500 people are
OL,19,Faffected, which is worth about #250m
OL,20,Fin overpayments.
