OL,6,FElizabeth Tait from Thames Ditton in
OL,7,FSurrey has a similar story. Her son
OL,8,FOliver has Down's Syndrome and needs
OL,9,Fround the clock care. She also cared
OL,10,Ffor her husband when he became
OL,11,Fterminally ill.
OL,13,FShe claimed the benefit but said she
OL,14,Funknowingly went over her hours while
OL,15,Fsupply teaching.
