OL,6,FThey, along with Elizabeth Tait and
OL,7,Fother unpaid carers, presented a
OL,8,Fdossier to the new minister Sir
OL,9,FStephen Timms in July, documenting up
OL,10,Fto 140 carers about their experiences
OL,11,Fof paying back their debt. In it, they
OL,12,Fheard from people who say they felt
OL,13,Flike criminals, really impacting their
OL,14,Fmental health and truly traumatic.
OL,16,FIn a Debate on the issue in Parliament
OL,17,Fthis October, Mel Stride, the Former
OL,18,Fwork and pensions secretary said
OL,19,F"there's an element of trust in how
OL,20,Fthat benefit works...therefore there
OL,21,Fis an earnings limit.
