OL,6,FLed by Liz Sayce, former CEO of
OL,7,FDisability Rights UK. It will focus on
OL,8,Fhow and why such debts were accrued,
OL,9,Fconsider what the department termed
OL,10,Foperational changes to minimise the
OL,11,Frisk of overpayment in future, and
OL,12,Flook at how people with overpayments
OL,13,Fcan best be supported.
OL,15,FBut Liberal Democrat leader Sir Ed
OL,16,FDavey insisted the majority of cases
OL,17,Fof overpayment should be "written off
